channel.title: Do they sound like cats?
channel.description:
Hey, I made a remix of an Animal Crossing song and the original has cats meowing in the background. I was working on the remix in Auxy 4 so obviously samples wasn’t an option.
https://soundcloud.com/plhector/1pm
Well? Do they sound like cats?
